OL,3,CPost Office 'dragging heels' as report
OL,4,Csays it's unfit to handle payouts
OL,6,FA former sub-post master, who ran a
OL,7,FPost Office in Leicestershire for 25
OL,8,Fyears, said she believes the company
OL,9,Fis "purposely dragging its heels" by
OL,10,Fnot paying out compensation.
OL,12,FJulie Beisner's family had ran a Post
OL,13,FOffice in Leicestershire since around
OL,14,F1847.
OL,16,FShe was brought up helping her
OL,17,Fgrandmother behind the counter and
OL,18,Flearning how to do accounts by hand -
OL,19,Fshe was born and raised to be a sub-
OL,20,Fpostmaster.
