OL,3,CPost Office 'dragging heels' as report
OL,4,Csays it's unfit to handle payouts
OL,6,FMs Beisner took on the running of the
OL,7,FPost Office in North Kilworth in 1996
OL,8,Fas sub-postmaster and ran it for
OL,9,Fnearly 25 years, before retiring in
OL,10,F2021.
OL,12,FDuring that time, the Post Office
OL,13,Fdemanded she make up alleged
OL,14,Fshortfalls in her accounts.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, a report released on
OL,17,FThursday 7 March has called for the
OL,18,FPost Office to be completely removed
OL,19,Ffrom overseeing compensation schemes
OL,20,Ffor victims, like Ms Beisner, of the
OL,21,FHorizon scandal.
