OL,3,CPost Office 'dragging heels' as report
OL,4,Csays it's unfit to handle payouts
OL,6,FMs Beisner told ITV News Central she
OL,7,Fbelieves the Post Office is purposely
OL,8,Fdragging its heels, as "the longer it
OL,9,Fholds out, the less of us there will
OL,10,Fbe around to pay".
OL,12,FPost Office minister, Kevin Hollinrake
OL,13,FMP, told the Commons on Thursday 7
OL,14,FMarch he agrees that compensation
OL,15,Fschemes should be brought in house.
OL,17,FHe said: "The scheme is already being
OL,18,Fdelivered by the Department of
OL,19,FBusiness and Trade.
